	<dl>
	<dt>Because it is the process by which idiots...</dt>
	<dd><p>Democracy sucks.<br />Why it sucks?<br />Because it is the process by which idiots are elected by the ignorant to govern a nation.</p>
	<small>
	written 8th Apr 2005 <!--  | <a href="../email/512">Email this
    to a friend</a> | <a
    href="/abuse/?postid=512">abusive?</a> -->
	</small>
	</dd>
